 joycon->uart\_intr.intr\_enable\_mask = UART\_RXFIFO\_FULL\_INT\_ENA\_M | UART\_RXFIFO\_TOUT\_INT\_ENA\_M | UART\_FRM\_ERR\_INT\_ENA\_M | UART\_RXFIFO\_OVF\_INT\_ENA\_M | UART\_BRK\_DET\_INT\_ENA\_M | UART\_PARITY\_ERR\_INT\_ENA\_M;
